snippet.title: Tearaway Unfolded - PlayStation Experience 2014 Trailer 60FPS
snippet.description:
From the creators of LittleBigPlanet comes Tearaway™ Unfolded – a mesmerizing adventure through a magical world of paper.

Coming to PlayStation 4, our latest trailer for Tearaway Unfolded is captured in a glorious 60 frames per second.

http://tearaway.mediamolecule.com
